## Technical checklist (new intent page)

1. Add entry to `INTENT_LANDINGS` in `intentLandings.js`
2. Thin `src/app/{path}/page.jsx` via `createIntentLandingPageExports(path)`
3. Sitemap entry in `sitemap.ts`
4. `relatedLinks` → other intent paths (renders as GuideCards)
5. `fetchIntentLandingParks` passes `pinned=featuredParkCodes.join(',')`
6. Dev fetch: `cache: 'no-store'`; production ISR 1h
7. Match reasons come from backend — fix traits in `server/src/catalog/traitBuilder.js` / `matchExplanation.js`, not in this file

---

## Editorial guides (`guides.js`)

- Slug under `/guides/[slug]`
- `GuideDetailClient`: hero (no image), TOC, quick answer, sections, FAQ, related guides
- No date badges on guide pages
- Tool links use friendly labels, not raw URLs in body copy

